===============================================
SECRETS & CONFIGURATION - DO NOT COMMIT
===============================================
Firebase configuration file. Contains sensitive API keys.
/app/google-services.json

App signing keys. If these leak, anyone can sign and release
malicious updates to your app.
*.jks
*.keystore
/build

